<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>bingo's log</title><link>https://www.binlog.cc/</link><description>bingo的个人博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><managingEditor>bingo084@outlook.com (bingo)</managingEditor><webMaster>bingo084@outlook.com (bingo)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:44:15 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.binlog.cc/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>使用 WebP 加速网站</title><link>https://www.binlog.cc/posts/speed-up-with-webp/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:44:15 +0800</pubDate><author>bingo</author><guid>https://www.binlog.cc/posts/speed-up-with-webp/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image"><img loading="eager" src="https://www.binlog.cc/posts/speed-up-with-webp/images/featured-image.webp" alt="使用 WebP 加速网站" title="使用 WebP 加速网站" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"/></div><p><a href="https://developers.google.com/speed/webp?hl=zh-cn"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">WebP<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a> 是 Google 开发的一种光栅图形文件格式，旨在替代 JPEG、PNG 和 GIF 文件格式。它支持有损和无损压缩，以及动画和 Alpha 透明度。</p>]]></description></item><item><title>我的日常</title><link>https://www.binlog.cc/logs/daily/</link><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 12:24:12 +0800</pubDate><author>bingo</author><guid>https://www.binlog.cc/logs/daily/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image"><img loading="eager" src="https://www.binlog.cc/logs/daily/images/featured-image.webp" alt="我的日常" title="我的日常" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"/></div><p>记录我的日常操作，包括工作、学习、生活等方面的内容。</p>]]></description></item><item><title>待办清单</title><link>https://www.binlog.cc/todolist/</link><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 09:53:31 +0800</pubDate><author>bingo</author><guid>https://www.binlog.cc/todolist/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image"><img loading="eager" src="https://www.binlog.cc/todolist/images/featured-image.webp" alt="待办清单" title="待办清单" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"/></div><p>我的待办清单</p>]]></description></item><item><title>Arch Linux 操作日志</title><link>https://www.binlog.cc/logs/archlinux/</link><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 22:43:10 +0800</pubDate><author>bingo</author><guid>https://www.binlog.cc/logs/archlinux/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image"><img loading="eager" src="https://www.binlog.cc/logs/archlinux/images/featured-image.webp" alt="Arch Linux 操作日志" title="Arch Linux 操作日志" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"/></div><p>记录我在 <code>Arch Linux</code> 下的日常操作</p>]]></description></item><item><title>配置 Linux 下的 FTP 服务</title><link>https://www.binlog.cc/posts/vsftpd/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 21:41:28 +0800</pubDate><author>bingo</author><guid>https://www.binlog.cc/posts/vsftpd/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image"><img loading="eager" src="https://www.binlog.cc/posts/vsftpd/images/featured-image.png" alt="配置 Linux 下的 FTP 服务" title="配置 Linux 下的 FTP 服务" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"/></div><p>这篇文章记录了我在 Linux 下使用 <a href="https://security.appspot.com/vsftpd.html" title="Probably the most secure and fastest FTP server for UNIX-like systems."target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">vsftpd<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a> 配置 FTP 服务的过程。</p>]]></description></item><item><title>纯净配置 Zsh</title><link>https://www.binlog.cc/posts/config-zsh/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 21:21:14 +0800</pubDate><author>bingo</author><guid>https://www.binlog.cc/posts/config-zsh/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image"><img loading="eager" src="https://www.binlog.cc/posts/config-zsh/images/featured-image.webp" alt="纯净配置 Zsh" title="纯净配置 Zsh" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"/></div><p>网上许多 <a href="https://www.zsh.org/" title="一款功能强大的命令行解释器（shell）"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Zsh<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>
的配置教程都是使用 <a href="https://ohmyz.sh/" title="a delightful, open source, community-driven framework for managing your Zsh configuration."target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">oh-my-zsh<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a> 来进行配置，
优点是配置起来<strong>简单</strong>，对新手友好，
缺点是太过<strong>臃肿</strong>，拖慢 Zsh 的启动速度。这篇文章记录了我不使用 oh-my-zsh 从零开始配置 Zsh 的过程。</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>